### Health
GET http://localhost:8000/health

### Run the full demo (triage all unassigned incidents)
POST http://localhost:8000/demo/run-all

### Routing stats dashboard
GET http://localhost:8000/stats

### Triage one incident (replace sys_id from demo output)
POST http://localhost:8000/triage/REPLACE_SYS_ID

### Webhook (what the ServiceNow Business Rule sends)
POST http://localhost:8000/webhook/incident
x-webhook-secret: change-me
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "sys_id": "REPLACE_SYS_ID",
  "number": "INC0010099",
  "short_description": "VPN not working from home",
  "description": "AnyConnect times out"
}
